    <string>TrainingLog 需要讀取 Apple Watch 訓練心率與消耗熱量、用於詳情頁統計。</string>
    <key>NSHealthUpdateUsageDescription</key>
    <string>TrainingLog 會在無 Apple Watch 紀錄時、把訓練 session 寫入健康資料，讓 Fitness App 顯示完整訓練紀錄。</string>
